OL,3,CVoters to cast ballots before polling
OL,4,Cday for first time under new trial
OL,6,FPeople will be able to vote before
OL,7,Fpolling day and in shopping centres
OL,8,Ffor the first time under a new
OL,9,Fgovernment pilot, which could change
OL,10,Fthe way we vote for the first time
OL,11,Fsince the Victorian era.
OL,13,FThe government trial will take place
OL,14,Fin four areas of England during the
OL,15,FMay 7 elections, giving voters the
OL,16,Fchoice of casting their ballot on more
OL,17,Fthan one day and at more than one
OL,18,Flocation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
