PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772568682
OL,3,CVoters to cast ballots before polling
OL,4,Cday for first time under new trial
OL,6,FThe way we vote hasn't changed since
OL,7,F1872, but this scheme is part of the
OL,8,Fgovernment's efforts to encourage more
OL,9,Fpeople to vote by modernising our
OL,10,Fvoting system in a trial that could be
OL,11,Frolled out nationally.
OL,13,FCurrently, people are only able to
OL,14,Fvote on one specific polling day,
OL,15,Feither at one designated local polling
OL,16,Fstation or by postal vote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
