PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772568682
OL,3,CVoters to cast ballots before polling
OL,4,Cday for first time under new trial
OL,6,FThe four locations where voters will
OL,7,Fhave the expanded voting options in
OL,8,FMay are Milton Keynes, Cambridge,
OL,9,FNorth Hertfordshire, and Tunbridge
OL,10,FWells.
OL,12,FIn Milton Keynes, people will be able
OL,13,Fto vote in the city's main shopping
OL,14,Fcentre, and in the three other areas,
OL,15,Fvoters will have the option of casting
OL,16,Ftheir ballot in person ahead of the
OL,17,Felection, including on the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
