OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772568682
OL,3,CVoters to cast ballots before polling
OL,4,Cday for first time under new trial
OL,6,FThe move is part of the government's
OL,7,Fefforts to deliver on a manifesto
OL,8,Fpledge to "encourage participation in
OL,9,Fdemocracy".
OL,11,FThe government says future pilots
OL,12,Fcould include mobile voting stations
OL,13,Fthat travel around communities,
OL,14,Fincluding to care homes and
OL,15,Funiversities.
OL,17,FMinisters insist the "integrity and
OL,18,Fsecurity" of the UK's voting system
OL,19,Fwill continue to be protected if the
OL,20,Freforms are rolled out nationally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
