OL,3,CVoters to cast ballots before polling
OL,4,Cday for first time under new trial
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FStarmer is also committed to lowering
OL,12,Fthe voting age to 16 and bringing in
OL,13,Ftougher rules on political donations
OL,14,Fand foreign interference as part of
OL,15,Fthe Representation of the People Bill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
