CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772568682
OL,3,CVoters to cast ballots before polling
OL,4,Cday for first time under new trial
OL,6,FMinister for Democracy Samantha Dixon
OL,7,Fsaid: "The way we vote in person has
OL,8,Fnot adapted to people's busy lives,
OL,9,Fwith voters often given no choice but
OL,10,Fto cast their ballot at strictly set
OL,11,Fpolling stations within limited hours.
OL,13,F"Our trials will make polling days
OL,14,Fmore convenient and test out the first
OL,15,Freal changes for over 100 years,
OL,16,Fbringing our democracy into the 21st
OL,17,Fcentury."
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
