PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772568682
OL,3,CVoters to cast ballots before polling
OL,4,Cday for first time under new trial
OL,6,FThe Association of Electoral
OL,7,FAdministrators welcomed the changes,
OL,8,FChief Executive Peter Stanyon said:
OL,9,F"Weekend and early voting, plus voting
OL,10,Fhubs at places like shopping centres,
OL,11,Fare used to good effect in many
OL,12,Fdemocracies and we hope will also be
OL,13,Fsuccessful here."
OL,15,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,16,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,17,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,18,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
